}

###ENABLE USER API KEY FEATURE
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/v1/enable/71b60b16-29c4-4483-92cb-29e3393c70c8
Authorization: Bearer {{admin}}

###DISABLE USER API KEY FEATURE
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/disable/3
Authorization: Bearer {{admin}}

###CREATE USER API KEY
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/create/key
Authorization: Bearer {{pj}}

###GET USER ACTIVE KEY
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/user/key
Authorization: Bearer {{pj}}


